       <div style="margin-top: 32px; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
         <a href="https://www.screenlux.de/products/zip-screen-configurator" class="mg2-btn mg2-btn-primary" id="btn-configure" style="opacity: 0.5; pointer-events: none;">Jetzt Screen konfigurieren &rarr;</a>
